  "text": "This section shows experimental results of the discussed methods for a simple two-source two-microphone situation. Since this paper is a review paper, detailed experimental results under a variety of conditions are not shown here. Such experimental results can be found in the original papers, e.g., [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The purpose of this section is to illustrate the characteristics of the reviewed five methods (ICA, IVA, ILRMA, NMF, MNMF).",
